A SHOCKING video has hit the internet. And people are calling for the woman in the video to be arrested as soon as possible. The video shows a woman dancing and having fun with a little girl. She shares a smoke and beer with her. In another instance, she puffs what she is smoking and blows the smoke at the little girl’s face. As much as she was enjoying every moment of it, people who have watched the video were left disgusted. Many called her an animal, saying she doesn’t deserve to be called a mother, although it’s unclear if it is her daughter. “She must be arrested, finish and klaar,” said a Facebooker called Sbu.